# TextInput — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/text-input.css`

## CSS Classes

### Structure
- `.acko-text-input` — flex column wrapper, gap-1
- `.acko-text-input-label` — label-lg typography tokens
- `.acko-text-input-wrapper` — flex row, border, rounded-full
- `.acko-text-input-el` — the actual `<input>` element

### Sizes (via `.acko-text-input-wrapper-{size}`)
| Size | Height | Padding | Font | Icon size |
|------|--------|---------|------|-----------|
| sm | `--scale-40` (h-10) | px-4 | `--font-body-sm-size` | `--font-body-sm-size` |
| md | `--scale-48` (h-12) | px-5 | `--font-body-md-size` | `--font-body-md-size` |
| lg | `--scale-56` (h-14) | px-6 | `--font-body-lg-size` | `--font-body-lg-size` |

### Variants / Children
- `.acko-text-input-icon-left` / `.acko-text-input-icon-right` — icon slots, sized to match the size variant's font token
- `.acko-text-input-prefix` / `.acko-text-input-suffix` — text addons
- `.acko-text-input-helper-text` / `.acko-text-input-error-text` — below input
- `.acko-text-input-char-count` — right-aligned character count
- `.acko-text-input-required` — red asterisk

### States (raw CSS)

| State | Border | Background | Label | Icon | Extra |
|-------|--------|-----------|-------|------|-------|
| `.acko-text-input-focused` | `--color-primary` + `0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary)` ring | `--color-surface` | `--color-primary` | `--color-primary` | Placeholder fades to `--color-text-disabled` (200ms ease) |
| `.acko-text-input-filled` | `--color-border-strong` (when value.length > 0, not focused) | `--color-surface` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-text-muted` | — |
| `.acko-text-input-error` | `--color-error` | `--color-surface` | `--color-error-text` | `--color-text-muted` | `animation: acko-shake 300ms ease-out` |
| `.acko-text-input-success` | `--color-border-strong` | `--color-surface` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-success` checkmark | Replaces `iconRight`; lucide `Check` icon, `strokeWidth: 2.5`; `animation: acko-check-pop 300ms ease-out` |
| `.acko-text-input-disabled` | `--color-disabled-border` | `--color-surface-raised` | `--color-text-muted` | `--color-text-disabled` | `cursor: not-allowed` |
| `.acko-text-input-readonly` | `--color-border-subtle` | `--color-surface-raised` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-text-muted` | Input text: `--color-text-secondary` |

### Character Count
- Displayed when `maxLength` prop is set
- Format: `{current}/{max}`
- Font: `--font-caption-size`, color `--color-text-muted`, right-aligned

### Transition Timing
All border/background/shadow transitions use `200ms ease`.

### Border Consistency Rule
All non-disabled input field borders MUST use `var(--color-input-border)` consistently. Only the disabled variant gets a toned-down border (`var(--color-border-subtle)` + muted bg). This ensures visual consistency across all input components (TextInput, Textarea, InputGroup, Dropdown).

### Dark Theme Overrides
Scoped under `[data-theme="dark"]`:
- Default wrapper bg: `--color-surface-raised` (not `--color-surface`)
- Disabled: bg `--color-disabled-bg`, border `--color-disabled-border`, text `--color-disabled-text`
- Error border: `--color-error`
- Success icon: `--color-success`
